The Dagger of the Chosen One
The Village Elder has taken the weapon of the Chosen One, a bronze dagger, from Babur. This item is close to Babur as a memento of his only friend. If this dagger is returned to him, the smith will produce a key with which to open the gate in the Middle Peaks.
#subobj 1
Cross the bridges
The only way to the sacred place where the Chosen One appeared is north of the swamp camp across two bridges.
#subobj 2
Go to the sacred ruins
The ruins are located on a high cliff in the west of this area. The passage to this location is well guarded.
#subobj 3
Take the dagger
The Chosen One's dagger lies along with his other belongings, kept in a chest in the Sacred Ruins.